author: Guerella

comments.content: Makes me think of what could happen if you slammed Dogma and FF Blur together.

I think the Emigre connection is close, because [Keedy Sans](http://web.archive.org/web/20150131192603/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/emigre/keedy-sans/) could have partly inspired this, in a sort of twisted way.

- Mike Yanega
I think this is (a) a very nice grunge-style hybrid sans and (b) a custom designed logo/typeface.
